==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nectar
<hw>Nec"tar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr. Gr.
<?/.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Myth. & Poetic)</fld> <def>The drink of
the gods (as ambrosia was their food); hence, any delicious or inspiring
beverage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A sweetish secretion of blossoms
from which bees make honey.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nectareal</ent>⟦br⟧
